propel.core.collections.buffers

Class LRUBuffer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.buffers.LRUBuffer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, IBuffer<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>

    public class LRUBuffer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBuffer<T>
    A type-aware least recently used (LRU) buffer. This collection does not allow nulls to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new LRUBuffer<String>(){}; -OR- new LRUBuffer<String>(String.class);
